snippet.title: [PSX] Zoids - Teikoku vs Kyouwakoku - Meka Seitai no Idenshi (Japan)
snippet.description: The intro movie is so well animated... and then you get to the game and the strategy game layer looks like a kid drew it. Also: dang, getting kicked does 2x as much damage as laser beams. Why even shoot anything.
